Currently a the support classes we inject into our {{SearchRequestView}} implementations are mostly concrete. We need 

From {{ContainerRegistrar}}:
{code}
register.implementation(INTERNAL, SearchRequestURLHandler.class);
register.implementation(INTERNAL, IssueViewURLHandler.class);
register.implementation(INTERNAL, SearchRequestHeader.class);
register.implementation(INTERNAL, SearchRequestPreviousView.class);
register.implementation(INTERNAL, SearchRequestViewBodyWriterUtil.class);
register.implementation(PROVIDED, VelocityRequestContextFactory.class, DefaultVelocityRequestContextFactory.class);
register.implementation(INTERNAL, IssueViewUtil.class);
{code}

All the above INTERNAL implementations need to be converted to interfaces and PROVIDED.

